reviewText: It's nothing like the original Awesome Pawsome.
Excellent! Only one better is the original.

I LOVE this movie! I have watched it several times. it never gets old! I would love to be able to go to AU some day, and see this big cat park! I must warn that the cute-ness factor is off the scale! You will enjoy it very much! One of the best big cat movie's out there, period! You NEED to see this! Thank You for quick ship and packaging well!!

I saw the original Awesome Pawsome and was convinced it was "the best" but this one is just as good.  I am in awe of the folks who work with these animals and have such relationships with them.  If you love big cats Get This One.  You won't regret it.
